Robert Feldman was the 20062007 GASC ASUCD Gender and Sexuality Commission Chair. He is a double major in Anthropology and Women and Gender Studies from La Mesa, California. He was also a clerk at the Specialized Transportation Services office as well as a former intern for former ASUCD Senate ASUCD Senator Kristen Birdsall.  Currently he works at the Marketplace General Nutrition Center (GNC).

Robert is probably the nicest person in California, and everyone he meets can attest to this. In fact, everyone he meets loves him, but he never believes it when told.
